title: Canaveral National Seashore: Park Statistics
body: Explore This Park    Learn About the Park     Management     Park Statistics              Park Statistics      Visitor use statistics for Canaveral National Seashore, as well as other National Parks are available through the National Park Service Statistics office website.  Here you can view public use records for individual National Parks, going back 10 years. Both monthly and annual reports are available. Click here  If you want to go directly to the statistical data page for Canaveral National Seashore click here.
